orms in warfare in the future.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aWar (International law). 7aHISTORY / General.2bisacsh1 aAndreopoulos, George J., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aAndreopoulos, George, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aBiddle, Tami Davis, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHattendorf, John B., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHoward, Michael, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKennedy, Paul, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aOber, Josiah, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aParker, Geoffrey, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRoberts, Adam, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRosenberg, David Alan, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRothenberg, Gunther, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSelesky, Harold E., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aShulman, Mark R., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aShulman, Mark R., eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aStacey, Robert C., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press eBook-Package Archive Pre-2000z978311053801440uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030017488540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300174885423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300174885/original  a978-3-11-053801-4  Yale University Press eBook-Package Archive Pre-2000b2000  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles